<div class = "row my-column-wrapper">

  <div class = "col-sm-12 col-md-4 my-intro-text">
    <h1>Best Cobwebs</h1>
    <p>Here at <em>The Cobweb Company</em> we serve only the finest and most delicate cobwebs from all over the world! </p>
    <p>
      From the large web of the deadly klingon cave crawler to the fragile net of the tiny paramecium spider, we have them all. Moreover, instead of presenting meaningless Lorem ipsum text, we share wisdom and beauty.
    </p>
  </div> <!-- end  column-->

  <div class = "col-sm-12 col-md-4 my-intro-text">
    <h1>Best Service</h1>
    <p> We keep your cobwebs fresh and shiny! Because we care and we can!</p>
    <p> If your cobwebs are sticky or broken, mail them in and we will send you a quote at no additional costs! All of our cobwebs come with full-satisfaction guarantee. If you are not content, we take them back without any question.</p>

  </div> <!-- end  column-->

  <div class = "col-sm-12 col-md-4">
    <div class = "my-badge-ani" id = "featuredBadge">Featured products</div>

    <div id = "myProductCarousel" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="4000">

      <!-- Indicators -->
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <% for ii in 0..@products.length-1%>
        <li data-target="#myProductCarousel" data-slide-to= "<%=ii%>" <%= "class = active" if ii == 0  %>></li>
        <%end%>
      </ol>

     <!-- Cards -->
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <% @products.each do |product| %>
        <div class="carousel-item<%= " active" if product == @products.first %>">
          <%= render partial: 'shared/my-product-card', locals: {myProduct: product, includeButtons: false} %>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- end  myProductCarousel-->
  </div> <!-- end  column-->
</div> <!-- end  row-->
